               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18410510-name-734" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18410510-name-734" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18410510-name-734" type="surname" value="COULSON"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18410510-name-734" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES COULSON</persName>
                  </hi>. I keep a marine store shop on Saffron-hill. On the evening of the 25th of April I found the prisoner at my counter with this chain—he said his mistress had sent him to sell it—I said I would go with him to his mistress, which I did—she denied having sent him, but said the chain was hers—I took him to the station, and on the road he said his father told him to take it—I said he was a very bad boy, and I could not believe him—I took him to the station.</p>
